### Crear un pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "cartId": 1
}

### Obtener todos los pedidos (solo admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un pedido espec√≠fico
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar pedido (cambiar cart o user)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "paid"
}

### Cambiar estado del pedido
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "shipped"
}

### Eliminar pedido
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
